query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('combinatorics',
'elementary-number-theory',
'general-topology',
'geometry',
'inequality',
'matrices',
'probability')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
